            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[# SuperScreenshot 0.9.86

- 短箭头先显示为圆头线段。
- 箭头头部从约 20px 开始平滑出现，并逐渐增长到完整形态。
- 优化箭身、圆角尾部与箭头头部的衔接。

---

- Renders very short arrows as rounded line segments.
- Smoothly grows the arrowhead from about 20px to its full shape.
- Refined the connection between the rounded shaft and arrowhead.
